			</div>
		</section>

		<Section title='About'>
			<p class='text-muted-foreground'>
				Full Stack Developer boasting over 5+ years of experience, specializing in technologies such
				as JavaScript, and Python. My journey includes dynamic contributions to banking,
				telecommunications, and oil & gas industries, where my innovative approach has left a
				lasting impact.
			</p>
		</Section>
